Package: pergola
Type: Package
Title: Toolbox for polyploid genetic data
Version: 1.0
Date: 2014-12-12
Authors@R: person("Fabian", "Grandke", email = "grafabian@gmail.com",
  role = c("aut", "cre")),
  person("Dirk", "Metzler", email = "metzler@bio.lmu.de",
  role = c("ths"))
Description: This package provides tools for linkage mapping in polyploids.
    It implements the method PERGOLA, which is a fast, deterministic method to
    calculate the order of markers in a linkage group.
License: GPL-3
Imports: 
    seriation,
    gtools
LazyData: true
